440
00:16:08,470 --> 00:16:10,060
Let's keep drinking.

441
00:16:11,320 --> 00:16:12,160
Come on.

442
00:16:12,750 --> 00:16:13,730
Here's to you.

443
00:16:15,800 --> 00:16:16,640
You...

