533
00:20:09,360 --> 00:20:11,920
You do! Chang Xinyi is your Moonlight.

534
00:20:11,920 --> 00:20:13,100
I really don't.

535
00:20:19,880 --> 00:20:20,720
You do.

536
00:20:23,880 --> 00:20:24,820
