566
00:21:50,750 --> 00:21:52,150
- You're a bathroom heater.
- Bathroom heater?

567
00:21:52,360 --> 00:21:53,440
No, you're Little Sunshine.

568
00:21:53,440 --> 00:21:54,300
- You...
